https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>已故说唱老将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fatman-scoop">法特曼·斯库普</a>的死因已经揭晓。</p><p>这位说唱歌手的真名是艾萨克·弗里曼 (Isaac Freeman)， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rap-icon-fatman-scoop-has-died-after-suffering-medical-emergency-on-stage-3789417">上个月末（8 月 30 日）在康涅狄格州表演时在舞台上晕倒后去世</a>。他今年 56 岁。</p><p>倒塌后，市长劳伦·加勒特在社交媒体上证实，弗里曼正被救护车送往医院。这位说唱歌手的巡演经理 DJ Pure Cold 后来在 Instagram 上发帖证实弗里曼已经去世。 </p><figure id="attachment_3789782" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3789782" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3789782" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="胖子勺。照片来源：Naomi Rahim/WireImage" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3789782" class="wp-caption-text">胖子勺。照片来源：Naomi Rahim/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>现在，在<a href="https://apnews.com/article/fatman-scoop-dead-heart-disease-d2df783c70779d9dcb9555440ba56fdd" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美联社</em></a>的一份新报道中，康涅狄格州法医办公室证实法特曼·斯库普死于心脏病。这位说唱歌手还患有高血压和动脉粥样硬化性心血管疾病，这是一种由动脉壁斑块堆积引起的心脏病。</p><p>在他去世的消息传出后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/missy-elliott-questlove-nicki-minaj-lead-tributes-to-fatman-scoop-truly-one-of-the-best-voices-in-hip-hop-3789732">几位说唱歌手和音乐家向这位已故的退伍军人表示敬意</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/missy-elliott">米西·埃利奥特 (Missy Elliott</a> ) 与弗里曼合作创作了 2005 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>奖获奖歌曲《Lose Control》， <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_VyaJZuDWT/?igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener">她在 Instagram 上分享了一段视频，</a>并配文：“Fatman Scoop 的声音和能量为这么多歌曲做出了贡献，这些歌曲让人们感到快乐并想为之跳舞。每次你听到它们都会超过[两]几十年。他的影响是巨大的，永远不会被忘记。”</p><p> Nicki Minaj <a href="https://x.com/celebslovenicki/status/1830360579233776084" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在她的 Instagram Stories 上</a>发布了一张 Fatman Scoop 的照片，并写道：“献给这位标志性、魅力十足、讨人喜欢的嘻哈传奇人物。愿您的灵魂得到完美的平静。你给这个世界带来了如此多的快乐。愿主赏赐你。” </p><figure id="attachment_3789420" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3789420" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3789420" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_fatmanscoop_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="胖子勺" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_fatmanscoop_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_fatmanscoop_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_fatmanscoop_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_fatmanscoop_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_fatmanscoop_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_fatmanscoop_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3789420" class="wp-caption-text"> Fatman Scoop 将于 2023 年 11 月 10 日在澳大利亚墨尔本 Rod Laver Arena 举办 Fridayz Live &#39;23 图片来源：Naomi Rahim/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>除了米西·埃利奥特之外，法特曼·斯库普多年来还与许多艺术家合作，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey">玛丽亚·凯莉</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janet-jackson">珍妮·杰克逊</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/whitney-houston">惠特尼·休斯顿</a>。他还出现在玛丽亚·凯莉的热门单曲“It&#39;s Like That”中，这使她获得了格莱美最佳流行女声表演奖。</p><p>这位说唱歌手与戴斯·佩索 (Dyce Payso) 合作的最新歌曲《Let It Go》的音乐视频在康涅狄格州演唱会前几个小时发布。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatman-scoops-cause-of-death-has-been-revealed-3797181">《Fatman Scoop》死因揭晓的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Thom Yorke 正在将 Radiohead 的《Hail To The Thief》改编成新的《哈姆雷特》作品https://www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-is-reworking-radioheads-hail-to-the-thief-for-new-hamlet-product-3797170?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=thom-约克正在改造无线电台，向小偷致敬，制作新的哈姆雷特Surej SinghThu, 26 Sep 2024 03:46:28 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3797170 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《哈姆雷特向小偷万岁》将于 2025 年 4 月在曼彻斯特首映</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-is-reworking-radioheads-hail-to-the-thief-for-new-hamlet-production-3797170">Thom Yorke 正在将 Radiohead 的《Hail To The Thief》改编成新作品《哈姆雷特》</a>的消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/thom-yorke@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thom-yorke">Thom Yorke</a>正在将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead</a> 2003 年的关键专辑《Hail To The Thief》改编成莎士比亚标志性戏剧<em>《哈姆雷特》</em>的新作品 - 了解更多信息，请参见下文。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/radiohead-kid-amnesiae-review-3087188">Radiohead – “Kid Amnesiae”评论：两张经典唱片的令人难忘的秘密历史</a></strong></li></ul><p>即将上映的作品名为<em>《哈姆雷特向小偷万岁</em>》，约克将与托尼奖和奥利维尔奖获奖导演史蒂文·霍格特和克里斯汀·琼斯合作，创作一部根据威廉·莎士比亚的<em>《哈姆雷特》</em>改编的当代作品。</p><p>在制作过程中，Yorke 将“亲自修改”并为 20 多名音乐家和演员精心编排《Hail To The Thief》，并在每场演出期间进行现场表演。该项目被描述为“一种狂热的新现场体验，融合了戏剧、音乐和动作”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3797172" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797172" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797172" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hamlet-hail-to-the-thief@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hamlet-hail-to-the-thief@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hamlet-hail-to-the-thief@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hamlet-hail-to-the-thief@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hamlet-hail-to-the-thief@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hamlet-hail-to-the-thief@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hamlet-hail-to-the-thief@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3797172" class="wp-caption-text"> 《哈姆雷特向小偷致敬》的艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><em>《哈姆雷特向小偷万岁》</em>的官方剧情如下：“埃尔西诺已成为一个监视国家，其公民的血液里流淌着忙碌的血液。 <em>《哈姆雷特向小偷万岁》讲述了</em>哈姆雷特和奥菲莉亚对丹麦的谎言和腐败的觉醒，这些谎言和腐败逐渐被鬼魂和音乐揭露。偏执狂盛行，没有人能幸免于悲剧性的崩溃。”</p><p>该作品将于明年 4 月 27 日在曼彻斯特的 Aviva Studios 举行全球首演，并将持续到 5 月 18 日，然后移师斯特拉特福皇家莎士比亚剧院，并于 6 月 4 日至 6 月 28 日上演。</p><p> <em>《哈姆雷特向小偷万岁》</em>的门票将于 10 月 2 日上午 10 点（英国夏令时）通过<a href="https://email.cisionone.cision.com/c/eJwUyEFOxSAQANDTlB3NMMDQLli4-dcwUGb8REqVkm-8vXH7SsTtcKA4moDBgscd1TMyWbJBKOWS2QGQCAdyB4FkzhhUjUTidrIliHXh3QRCAbQbyrY4uGvhz_qtz1Qbj1vvJJv3Puz6Pia-1n9XLT7n_Frs24KPBR-SjnmN39onj55mvXpq6zU-1Iipl8E_6xzcC7e2OOgnr8d1qnsO5lPXEo14IAOi2WTSzmTUma3TPjtDSGXPENQr4l8AAAD__7oHSSI" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://email.cisionone.cision.com/c/eJwUyEFOxSAQANDTlB3NMMDQLli4-dcwUGb8REqVkm-8vXH7SsTtcKA4moDBgscd1TMyWbJBKOWS2QGQCAdyB4FkzhhUjUTidrIliHXh3QRCAbQbyrY4uGvhz_qtz1Qbj1vvJJv3Puz6Pia-1n9XLT7n_Frs24KPBR-SjnmN39onj55mvXpq6zU-1Iipl8E_6xzcC7e2OOgnr8d1qnsO5lPXEo14IAOi2WTSzmTUma3TPjtDSGXPENQr4l8AAAD__7oHSSI&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1727398354064000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3Ou4nDHQ55pE83jh7YJuiR">factoryinternational.org</a>和<a href="https://email.cisionone.cision.com/c/eJwUyLFywyAMANCvMRucEEKCgaFLfqNnjGh8sZMWu_Hv97q-VjAtBEaLF5QAETOaeyEmiQk9paU2yRlVYkszwIxROSWzFuZOmUOTHkg-vTB2wJCwp4ngWJs-1h-7z-um47CZe4oxSrbHcuLb_bvZyv08v6fwMeFtwtt1XW4ci3uNL_f7MKPMzzb0cufQZ9Ntmwieu7rltZvjHKq7XVvxPQJ76FZ9ZUu-oq0ayMZKnpFbriDmXfAvAAD__4TQQ1w" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://email.cisionone.cision.com/c/eJwUyLFywyAMANCvMRucEEKCgaFLfqNnjGh8sZMWu_Hv97q-VjAtBEaLF5QAETOaeyEmiQk9paU2yRlVYkszwIxROSWzFuZOmUOTHkg-vTB2wJCwp4ngWJs-1h-7z-um47CZe4oxSrbHcuLb_bvZyv08v6fwMeFtwtt1XW4ci3uNL_f7MKPMzzb0cufQZ9Ntmwieu7rltZvjHKq7XVvxPQJ76FZ9ZUu-oq0ayMZKnpFbriDmXfAvAAD__4TQQ1w&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1727398354064000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2zsI9SZsoRhYEt5E4fozhO">rsc.org.uk</a>发售。</p><p>约克在一份新闻声明中谈到<em>《哈姆雷特向小偷万岁》</em>时说道：“这是一个有趣而又令人生畏的挑战！将《小偷万岁》的原创音乐改编成现场表演，与舞台上的演员一起讲述这个永远被讲述的故事，利用它的熟悉性和声音，将它们带入和脱离上下文，看看什么与潜在的悲伤相呼应以及<em>哈姆雷特</em>的偏执，将音乐作为房间中的“存在”，观察它如何与动作和文本相碰撞。鬼影一个人对抗另一个人。” </p><figure id="attachment_3761685" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3761685" style="width: 1392px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3761685" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ThomYorke-TheSmile2024-Getty.jpg" alt="Thom Yorke 2024 现场表演《微笑》" width="1392" height="884" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ThomYorke-TheSmile2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ThomYorke-TheSmile2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ThomYorke-TheSmile2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ThomYorke-TheSmile2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ThomYorke-TheSmile2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3761685" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年 3 月，汤姆·约克 (Thom Yorke) 与微笑乐团 (The Smile) 在伦敦亚历山德拉宫演出。图片来源：Samir Hussein/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> Radiohead 的《Hail To The Thief》是乐队的第六张专辑，收录了《2 + 2 = 5》、《Go To Sleep》、《There There》、《A Punchup At A Wedding》等歌曲。乐队的第九张也是最新的录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/radiohead-a-moon-shaped-pool-talking-points-8462">《A Moon Shaped Pool》</a>于 2016 年发行，而他们最后一次一起巡演是在 2018 年。</p><p>本月早些时候，乐队贝斯手 Colin Greenwood <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-have-been-back-together-rehearsing-it-was-really-fun-3791835">透露 Radiohead 最近又一起排练</a>：“我们大约两个月前在伦敦进行了一些排练，只是为了演奏老歌。而且真的很有趣，度过了一段非常愉快的时光。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-have-been-back-together-rehearsing-it-was-really-fun-3791835"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>与此同时，由 Radiohead 的 Thom Yorke 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jonny-greenwood">Jonny Greenwood</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sons-of-kemet">Sons Of Kemet</a>鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-skinner">Tom Skinner</a>组成的 Radiohead 副项目<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smile">The Smile</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-smile-announce-new-album-cutouts-with-two-singles-foreign-spies-and-zero-sum-3788255">宣布了他们的新专辑《Cutouts》</a> （ <a href="https://thesmile.x-l.co/cutouts" target="_blank" rel="noopener">10 月 4 日发行</a>），并分享了两首新单曲《Foreign Spies》和《Zero Sum》 &#39;。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-is-reworking-radioheads-hail-to-the-thief-for-new-hamlet-production-3797170">Thom Yorke 正在将 Radiohead 的《Hail To The Thief》改编成新作品《哈姆雷特》</a>的消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
