h-Klinghoffer-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>前<a href="/artists/Red-Hot-Chili-Peppers">红辣椒</a>乐队吉他手乔什·克林霍夫将于本周因一场导致一人死亡的事故而被提审。</p><ul class="ul1 post-content-read-more"><li class="li1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/red-hot-chili-peppers-cover-interview-2022-unlimited-love-3152682"><b><em>NME</em>大读 - Red Hot Chili Peppers：“我们感觉新鲜，就像一支新乐队”</b></a></li></ul><p>这位音乐家还曾与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janes-addiction">Jane&#39;s Addition</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">Iggy Pop</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/morrissey">Morrissey</a>等乐队一起演出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-red-hot-chili-peppers-guitarist-sued-for-wrongful-death-in-driving-accident-3773867" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此前因涉嫌撞倒行人而被控过失致死和过失罪</a>。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/red-hot-chili-peppers-josh-klinghoffer-sued-for-wrongful-death-1236066239/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>和<a href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/07/10/red-hot-chili-peppers-josh-klinghoffer-sued-wrongful-death-accused-running-over-killing-pedestrian-walking-crosswalk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>TMZ</em></a>报道，这起事件于 3 月 18 日发生在加利福尼亚州阿罕布拉，诉讼由 47 岁受害者以色列桑切斯的家人提起。</p><p>该诉讼称，克林霍夫在驾驶 SUV 时打电话。报道还称，当克林霍夫左转时，桑切斯正在一个有标记的十字路口过马路。桑切斯被车撞后伤重不治身亡。</p><p>现在，据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/09/josh-klinghoffer-vehicular-homicide-arraignment-1236099038/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a>报道，克林霍夫将于明天（9 月 26 日）因无重大过失的车辆过失杀人轻罪指控而受审。他将于太平洋时间上午 8:30（英国夏令时间下午 4:30）在加利福尼亚州阿罕布拉法院提出抗辩。 </p><figure id="attachment_3797130" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797130" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797130" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1.jpg" alt="乔什·克林霍夫 (Josh Klinghoffer) 在加利福尼亚州英格尔伍德的 SoFi 体育场举行的全球公民 VAX LIVE：世界重聚音乐会上登台表演。 （凯文·温特/盖蒂图片社为 Global Citizen VAX LIVE 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Josh-Klinghoffer-performing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3797130" class="wp-caption-text">乔什·克林霍夫 (Josh Klinghoffer) 在加利福尼亚州英格尔伍德的 SoFi 体育场举行的全球公民 VAX LIVE：世界重聚音乐会上登台表演。 （凯文·温特/盖蒂图片社为 Global Citizen VAX LIVE 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>在 7 月份分享给<a href="https://pitchfork.com/news/former-red-hot-chili-peppers-guitarist-josh-klinghoffer-facing-wrongful-death-lawsuit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Pitchfork 的</em></a>一份声明中，克林霍夫的律师安德鲁·B·布雷特勒 (Andrew B. Brettler) 表示：“这是一场悲惨的事故。汽车撞上行人后，乔什立即靠边停车，拨打 911，等待警察和救护车到达。他正在全力配合交通调查。”</p><p>桑切斯家庭的律师尼克·罗利 (Nick Rowley) 向<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/red-hot-chili-peppers-josh-klinghoffer-sued-for-wrongful-death-1236066239/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》杂志</em></a>声称，他们“手机里有他击杀伊斯雷尔·桑切斯时的视频”。</p><p>他继续说道：“以色列·桑切斯正在去杂货店为家人做汤的路上，却再也没有回家。他所做的一切都是正确的，寻找迎面而来的车辆并遵守行人标志，但悲惨的是，克林霍夫先生在匆忙中打电话，用一辆大型SUV从后面撞死了他。桑切斯一家现在面临着巨大的损失和悲伤。在桑切斯先生及其家人得到问责和伸张正义之前，我们不会停止。”</p><p>克林霍夫于 2009 年至 2019 年在红辣椒队担任吉他手，2020 年，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-announce-john-frusciante-is-rejoining-band-2587514">宣布将在 10 年后离开红辣椒队</a>。他后来说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/josh-klinghoffer-no-hard-feelings-red-hot-chili-peppers-departure-2598495">他和乐队之间没有任何芥蒂</a>。后来他被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-john-frusciante-perform-first-time-12-years-2606617#:~:text=He's%20back!&amp;text=Footage%20has%20surfaced%20of%20Red,leaving%20the%20band%20in%202008.&amp;text=In%20December%2C%20the%20band%20announced,subsequently%20replaced%20by%20Josh%20Klinghoffer.">长期会员约翰·弗鲁西安特 (John Frusciante) 取代</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-red-hot-chili-peppers-guitarist-josh-klinghoffer-to-be-arraigned-for-vehicular-manslaughter-3797123">前红辣椒吉他手 Josh Klinghoffer 因车辆过失杀人罪被提审的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
